# The 1858-entry Lc0 policy index <-> UCI move map is small (~17 KB) and
# required for the policy net to produce non-uniform priors. Commit it
# alongside the code rather than shipping it via Releases.
!data/lc0_policy_map.txt
.accuracy_cache.json
data/books/
!data/blindspot_g10.epd
dev/sprt_runs/
